import React from 'react';
import {
    Container,
    Card,
    Button,
    Row,
    Col
  } from 'react-bootstrap';

  const Login = () => {
    return(
        <>
        <Container>
            <Card>
              <Row>
            Username:
            </Row>
            <Row>
              Password:
            </Row>
            <Row>
              
            <Col>
            <Button>Login</Button>
            </Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
            Don't Have an Account? 
            </Row>
            <Row>
            <Button>Sign Up Here!</Button>
            </Row>
           
            </Card>
            
        </Container>
        </>
    )
  }

export default Login;
